Data Types¶

LinkedListElement¶

A node in the linked list deneme.

typedef struct LinkedListElement
{
    void *data;
    struct LinkedListElement *next;
    struct LinkedListElement *prev;
} LinkedListElement;
LinkedList¶

The main data structure used to store a collection of elements of type LinkedListElement. It basically contains pointers to the head and tail elements:

typedef struct LinkedList
{
 struct LinkedListElement *head;
 struct LinkedListElement *tail;
} LinkedList;
